<h2 id=3D"id-03:SD:InitiateNPPpaymenttoPayIDbeneficiary(Customer)[ERM25E2Fe=
bruary2025]-TechnicalDebt">Technical Debt</h2>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<h1 id=3D"id-03:SD:InitiateNPPpaymenttoPayIDbeneficiary(Customer)[ERM25E2Fe=
bruary2025]-Solution"><span>Solution</span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"id-03:SD:InitiateNPPpaymenttoPayIDbeneficiary(Customer)[ERM25E2Fe=
bruary2025]-SolutionOverview"><span>Solution Overview</span></h2>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col>
<col>
<col>
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Implementations</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Steps</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Details</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Updating Payee Addresbook with new Payee (with P=
ayID details)</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol>
<li>Use existing Payee INF endpoint</li>
<li>Use existing payee group ID.&nbsp;</li>
<li>Create new payload for payees to add</li>
</ol></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Refer to <a href=3D"/display/ARTC/Archived+01.+S=
D%3A+Beneficiary+%28Payee%29+Address+Book">Archived 01. SD: Beneficiary (Pa=
yee) Address Book</a> for group ID mapping&nbsp;</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Resolving the Payee PayID details using Alias Lo=
okup</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol>
<li>Implement Alias Resultion APIPOST&nbsp; <span class=3D"opblock-summary-=
path" style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);"><a class=3D"nostyle" style=3D"text-de=
coration: inherit;" rel=3D"nofollow"><span>/alias/lookup</span></a></span><=
/li>
<li>Filter out creditor bsb + accountNumber in EXP Response</li>
<li>Possible scenarios:=20
<ol>
<li>PayID resolves, matches Payee name =3D <span style=3D"color: rgb(51,153=
,102);">no&nbsp; UI message, enable submit button</span></li>
<li>PayID resolves,&nbsp; does not matches Payee name&nbsp; =3D<span style=
=3D"color: rgb(255,102,0);"> show </span><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,153,1=
02);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,102,0);">UI message</span>, enable subm=
it button</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,153,102);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0=
);">PayID does not resolve, due to technical 4xx/5xx <span style=3D"color: =
rgb(51,51,51);">erro</span></span><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);">r</=
span> =3D </span><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,102,0);">show </span><span s=
tyle=3D"color: rgb(51,153,102);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,102,0);">UI =
message</span>, <span style=3D"color: rgb(255,102,0);"><strong>disable </st=
rong>submit button</span></span></li>
<li>PayID does not resolve, because it is not registered<span style=3D"colo=
r: rgb(51,153,102);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,102,0);"> =3D&nbsp;</spa=
n></span><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,102,0);">show </span><span style=3D"=
color: rgb(51,153,102);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,102,0);">UI message<=
/span>, <span style=3D"color: rgb(255,102,0);"><strong>disable </strong>sub=
mit button</span></span></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>Pseudo to match Selected Payee name and Alias name:</p>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">entities=
.payees[x].name =3D=3D entities.lookup[0].name</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
